[ProMED is grateful for Dr. Ippolito's further clarification of the
misleading original popular press report and the translation error of
it. ProMED regrets any misunderstanding of the West Nile virus
situation in Italy so far this year (2010) that the original report
may have created for our subscribers.

Maps of the Emilia-Romagna and Lombardy regions in northern Italy can
be accessed at
<http://goeurope.about.com/cs/italy/l/bl_italy_region.htm>. The
HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Italy can be accessed at
<http://healthmap.org/r/01iJ>. - Mod.TY]
